title: NBA Over/Unders, Part 2: The West With Ryen Russillo and Joe House
description:
In Part 2 of a two-part podcast, The Ringer’s Bill Simmons is joined by Ryen Russillo and Joe House for the annual NBA Over/Unders pod. They run through win totals for each team in the Western Conference and look at odds for the NBA awards.

Host: Bill Simmons
Guests: Ryen Russillo and Joe House
Producer: Kyle Crichton
